			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2278367">
									

<p>Yep, they are directly from the RP's notes. I liked the detail, so I stole it, but I didn't realize that you'd created them.</p>
<p>I'm sorry the tale didn't work for you, though.</p>
<p>Regarding the ending:</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">show&nbsp;commentary</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>A lot of the way it's constructed relates to Council dynamics that I tried to imply more than directly state. I didn't want to make everything too on the nose in the story. And also, length was a concern. But if it didn't come across for you, it didn't come across.</p>
<p>I hope it works for others.</p>
</div>
