<p>Really, just awesome. Lots of cool little mini-stories, all tied into a long, suspenseful arc, and with how things have gone with responses to the Resurrection series, I felt that the ending could have truly gone either way.</p>
<p>Well written, to say the least. A good ending to this section of the series, leaving the audience ready and eager for the next season to start up.</p>
<p>+1</p>

